libkinect_aux
=============

About
-----
Kinect Auxiliary Library
Provides easy access to kinect acceleration sensor, motor and LED

Requirements
------------------
	- CMake  ( http://cmake.org/ )
	- libusb ( http://www.libusb.org/ )
	- kinect sensor

Compilation
-----------
	- mkdir build
	- cd build
	- cmake ../
	- make
	generated files:
	    - kinect_aux library
	  	- libkinect_aux.so    (Linux)
	  	- libkinect_aux.dylib (Mac OS X)
	    - test program
	      	- test                (Executable)

(to be changed in future commits)
